author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Gamestop Terminates Employment Of Tony Bartel And Michael Hogan, Effective Immediately​
text:
February 9, 2018 / 1:57 PM / in 6 minutes BRIEF-Gamestop Terminates Employment Of Tony Bartel And Michael Hogan, Effective Immediately​ Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 9 (Reuters) - Gamestop Corp: 
* GAMESTOP-ON FEB. 7, UPON AUTHORIZATION OF BOARD OF DIRECTORS, CO TERMINATED EMPLOYMENT OF TONY D. BARTEL AND MICHAEL P. HOGAN, EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY​ Source text: ( bit.ly/2Eb7z3M ) Further company coverage:
